  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_63",
    "english": "A UFS Officer. Former UFS Navy Special Forces, now a member of the UFS Department of State Task Force \"G\". The name \"Major\" is a code name, and her real name is still unknown.\n\nEvery muscle in her body is strengthened by a special metal fiber, endowing her entire body with the defense of an armored car and strength enough to beat up and kill a man-eating Ogre with her bare hands. Her main weapon is a baseball bat made of a special metal that even Major herself cannot dent.\n",
    "japanese": "A UFS Officer. Former UFS Navy Special Forces, now a member of the UFS Department of State Task Force \"G\". The name \"Major\" is a code name, and her real name is still unknown.\n\nEvery muscle in her body is strengthened by a special metal fiber, endowing her entire body with the defense of an armored car and strength enough to beat up and kill a man-eating Ogre with her bare hands. Her main weapon is a baseball bat made of a special metal that even Major herself cannot dent.\n",
    "korean": "A UFS Officer. Former UFS Navy Special Forces, now a member of the UFS Department of State Task Force \"G\". The name \"Major\" is a code name, and her real name is still unknown.\n\nEvery muscle in her body is strengthened by a special metal fiber, endowing her entire body with the defense of an armored car and strength enough to beat up and kill a man-eating Ogre with her bare hands. Her main weapon is a baseball bat made of a special metal that even Major herself cannot dent.\n",
    "chinese_simplified": "A UFS Officer. Former UFS Navy Special Forces, now a member of the UFS Department of State Task Force \"G\". The name \"Major\" is a code name, and her real name is still unknown.\n\nEvery muscle in her body is strengthened by a special metal fiber, endowing her entire body with the defense of an armored car and strength enough to beat up and kill a man-eating Ogre with her bare hands. Her main weapon is a baseball bat made of a special metal that even Major herself cannot dent.\n",
    "chinese_traditional": "A UFS Officer. Former UFS Navy Special Forces, now a member of the UFS Department of State Task Force \"G\". The name \"Major\" is a code name, and her real name is still unknown.\n\nEvery muscle in her body is strengthened by a special metal fiber, endowing her entire body with the defense of an armored car and strength enough to beat up and kill a man-eating Ogre with her bare hands. Her main weapon is a baseball bat made of a special metal that even Major herself cannot dent.\n",
    "spanish": "A UFS Officer. Former UFS Navy Special Forces, now a member of the UFS Department of State Task Force \"G\". The name \"Major\" is a code name, and her real name is still unknown.\n\nEvery muscle in her body is strengthened by a special metal fiber, endowing her entire body with the defense of an armored car and strength enough to beat up and kill a man-eating Ogre with her bare hands. Her main weapon is a baseball bat made of a special metal that even Major herself cannot dent.\n"
